Mou douleyoun:
H entolh exit kai cd
Oi aples entoles xoris pipes kai redirections

Den mou douleyoun:
Ta pipes
Ta redirections
Ta Shortcuts

Sto arxeio cs345sh.c h main periexei mia while h opoia se kathe epanalici tiponei to minima tou cmd 
me to userID kai to current working directory. 

Diabazetai mia grami apo to stdin kai (meso ths tokenizeThePipe) oi entoles xorizontai opou iparxei ">" kai 
meta apothikeyontai se ena array of String. 

Meta h execCommands pernei san orisma ayto to array xorizei thn mia entoli se tokens meso ths tokenizeTheLine kai ektelei tis entoles analoga.

Epishs to arxeio helpers.c periexei thn ilopoihsh kapoiwn synarthseon pou tha mporousan na xrhsimopoihthoun apo to cs345sh.c, 
(opos synarthseis gia na katalavoume an i entolh pou edose o xrhsths apo to stdin periexei redirections h pipes)
kai sto arxeio helpers.h  yparxoun oi ypografes gia tis synarthseis pou xrhsimopoiountai sto helpers.c (to interface tou arxeiou helpers.c).


